      </a>
      :
      <b>
       wn vr nn-mnmlsts
      </b>
     </h2>
     <div class="entry">
      <p>
       <img alt="" src="http://mnmlist.com/fotos/20090907frustration.jpeg"/>
       <small>
        Pht crtsy f
        <a href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/32289786@N05/3325230784/">
         hnnhlh14
        </a>
        .
       </small>
      </p>
      <p>
       <a href="http://mnmlist.com/about/#leo">
        By L
       </a>
      </p>
      <p>
       On f th bggst chllngs fr nyn wntng t lv  mnmlst lf s nt ntrnl bt xtrnl — thr lvd ns rn’t n brd th mnmlst trn.
      </p>
      <p>
       Hw d y dl wth tht? Wht’s th smpl sltn?
      </p>
      <p>
       Thr sn’t n.
      </p>
      <p>
       Dlng wth thrs wh mght b hrdrs, clttr-bgs, jst pln mssy, r myb jst rglr ppl wh dn’t cr bt mnmlsm … t’s nt sy. It’s s mch sr t lv ln nd nt hv t wrry bt th lvng hbts nd prfrncs f thrs, bt mny f s dn’t hv tht “lxry” (lthgh thr r  fw bnfts f lvng wth ths wh lv y).
      </p>
      <p>
       Hr r sm strtgs tht hv wrkd fr m. Yr mlg wll dfntly vry.
       <br/>
       <span id="more-159">
       </span>
       <br/>
       <strong>
        1. Fcs n yrslf
       </strong>
       . Whl yr sps r prtnr r chldrn my nt wnt t dclttr thr lvs r lv wtht cnsmrsm, y cn, t lst n th rs y cntrl. Y cn stp byng. Y cn gt rd f thngs y prsnlly wn tht y dn’t nd. Y cn fnd jy n dng rthr thn wnng r byng. Y cn rdc wht y d, wht y cnsm, wht y t, nd s n. Ths y cntrl, nd thy shld b yr frst fcs. Smtms, t wll b yr nly fcs, f th strtgs blw dn’t wrk.
      </p>
      <p>
       <strong>
        2. Ld by xmpl
       </strong>
       . Y mst rmmbr tht thrs r ppl wth thr wn blfs nd wy f lvng — whch y cnnt cntrl. Hwvr, y cn nflnc thm. And n f th bst wys f nflncng thrs s by xmpl. Lv  lf f mnmlsm, nd shw hw wndrfl t cn b. Shw hw sy — nd ctlly fn — t cn b t dclttr. Shw hw hppy y r. Shr t ll wth ths rnd y. D t wtht tryng t psh t n thm, bcs thy wll rct ngtvly t bng frcd r nggd nt dng nythng.
      </p>
      <p>
       <strong>
        3. Edct
       </strong>
       . Oftn ppl r gnst chng bcs thy dn’t knw ngh bt t. Cmbt ths gnrnc wth nn-pshy dctn. Tlk wth yr lvd ns bt wht y’r dng nd why. Shw thm xmpls f ppl wh nspr y. Snd thm lnks t mnmlsm.cm, Zn Hbts nd thr blgs nd mgzns y njy — nt s  hnt, bt s  wy t shr thngs y’r xctd bt. Ovr tm, thy’ll strt t ndrstnd, nd myb vn jn y.
      </p>
      <p>
       <strong>
        4. Ask fr hlp
       </strong>
       . Yr lvd ns, mst lkly, cr bt y. Thy wnt y t b hppy — bt wnt t b hppy thmslvs. Enlst yr lvd ns’ dsr t mk y hppy … sk thm fr hlp. Sy, “I nd yr hlp n gttng t th mnmlst lf I wnt. D y thnk y cn hlp m?” Of crs, f y’v dctd thm, thy lrdy knw wht y wnt, bt mst ppl wld lv t hlp y f thy cn. Dn’t sk thm t chng, bt sk f thy cn hlp y dclttr, r kp  crtn r nclttrd, r fgr t  sltn t  prblm y’r fcng.
      </p>
      <p>
       <strong>
        5. St bndrs
       </strong>
       . If y cn’t gt  lvd n n brd, t hlps t st bndrs. Fr kds, sk thm t kp thr clttr t thr rms. Gv thm tht prsnl spc, nd dn’t bg thm bt t. Fr dlts, y mght dsgnt crtn rms r rs s yrs nd thrs s thrs. I’v knwn sm ppl wh’v splt rms r ntr hms n hlf — n sd s nclttrd, nd th thr ws … nt.
      </p>
      <p>
       <strong>
        6. Fnd cmprmss
       </strong>
       . Lvng wth thr ppl mns fndng wys f lvng tht wrk fr vryn. Tht mght mn y nd t gv  lttl, f y wnt t sk thm t gv  lttl n rtrn. B wllng t ccpt  lss-thn-prfct sltn, f th sltn wll wrk fr vryn.
      </p>
      <p>
       <strong>
        7. Fnd ccptnc
       </strong>
       . In th nd, y mght nt wn vr th ppl wh lv wth y — nd y cn thr b frstrtd r ngry wth tht, r y cn ccpt t. Th scnd ptn s prfrrd, s y’ll hv mr pc f mnd. It’s nt sy, nd wll rqr y lttng g f crtn xpcttns, lttng g f  nd t cntrl, nd lrnng t lv smn fr wh thy r, nt wh y wnt thm t b. Bt n th nd, th ffrt wll b wrth t.
      </p>
